<p>Losing a friend is like losing a piece of yourself.  These messages offer gentle support and acknowledge the unique bond shared with the deceased. They are designed to bring comfort and understanding to a grieving friend.</p>
<li>I'm so deeply sorry for your loss.  [Name] will be greatly missed.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending my love during this challenging time.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need, now and in the days ahead.</li>
<li>[Name]'s memory will always be cherished.</li>
<li>Sending strength and peace your way.</li>
<li>Your friendship meant so much to [Name], and to me.</li>
<li>I'll always remember [Name]'s [positive quality].</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories you shared bring you comfort.</li>
<li>I’m heartbroken for your loss. Please let me know if there’s anything I can do.</li>
